value.name: Get_data_alert
value.description:
Get a list of alerts generated by Netskope. You can filter by timeperiod, alert type, acknowledged, or advanced query parameters.
This endpoint allows you to check all the Netskope Alerts in your tenant.
value.descriptionForModel:
Get a list of alerts generated by Netskope. You can filter by timeperiod, alert type, acknowledged, or advanced query parameters.
This endpoint allows you to check all the Netskope Alerts in your tenant.
examplePrompts: Show me all the Netskope Alerts for last 90 days for DLP.
Show me all the Netskope Alerts for last 3 days.
Show me the Netskope Alerts for Monday Oct 23 UTC for uba.
Show me all Netskope Malware Alerts for the last week.
Show me all Netskope Compromised Credential Alerts for the last 3 days.
Show me all Netskope Compromised Credential Alerts for last 24 hours.
Show me all Netskope Compromised Credential Alerts for last 24 hours with user exampleUser@netskope.com.

inputs.name: type
inputs.description: Alert type you would like to filter on

inputs.name: acked
inputs.description: Filter alerts by acknowledged status

inputs.name: limit
inputs.description: Max number of records to retrieve

inputs.name: offset
inputs.description: Used to shift the window of alerts if limit is reached

inputs.name: starttime
inputs.description: Unix timestamp of start time period of alerts

inputs.name: endtime
inputs.description: Unix timestamp of end time period of alerts

inputs.name: insertionstarttime
inputs.description: Restrict alerts which have been inserted into the database after the specified time. Always same as starttime.

inputs.name: insertionendtime
inputs.description: Restrict alerts which have been inserted into the database before the specified time. Always same as endtime.
